	<br>
	<br>
	<hr style="color:#cccccc;height:3px">
	<b>Advanced settings</b> <br /><br/>
	Updates from the following category are installed at your own risk.
	<br>
	<br>
	<input type="checkbox" id="eBetaLink" class="checkbox"><label for="eBetaLink"><b>Show beta products and related updates</b></label><br>
	<div class="spacer" style="HEIGHT: 5px"></div>
	<div class="OptionText">Display pre-release or "beta" products (software), or updates to beta software. Note that these updates should not be installed on your primary computer.</div>
	<br /> 
	<hr style="color:#cccccc;height:3px">
	<b>Other Settings</b> <br /><br>
	<input type="checkbox" id="eNewsLink" class="checkbox" checked ><label for="eNewsLink"><b>Show Windows Update news on home page</b></label><br>
	<div class="spacer" style="HEIGHT: 5px"></div>
	<div class="OptionText">The Windows update home page can display news about updates or this site that may be of interest to you. If you select this checkbox and do not see news on the home page, there is no current news to display.</div>
